org.wrml.schema
Class Field<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.wrml.util.Identifiable<T>
      org.wrml.schema.Member<String>
          org.wrml.schema.Field<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Identifiable<String>>, Unique<String>
public final class Field<T>
extends Member<String>

A web resource schema's field. Conceptually a field is a typed data slot, like a field in a Java object or a field on a web form. Instances of this class group the metadata associated with a specific schema's field.

See Also:
Serialized Form
